-- Encana to sell Bighorn gas assets for C$2 billion
-- 
-- Fri Jun 27, 2014 07:14AM EDT
-- None



June 27 (Reuters) - Encana Corp <ECA.TO>, Canada's largest natural gas producer, said it would sell its Bighorn gas properties in Alberta to Apollo Global Management LLC <APO.N> for about C$2 billion ($1.9 billion).

